name: Experiment Or Die #120
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Being able to communicate to one another is the prime factor in the exchange of information and connecting with other people. Different subsets of people have developed their own visual language and one of those groups of people are hobos. They have developed their own series of icons and symbols that help them passively communicate vital information to one another. The symbols emerged from necessity and common sense and if you open your eyes more often you'd probably see a whole world of language and culture that you have overlooked for most of your life. This double arrow symbol is quite important...warning of danger. Literally means Get The Fuck Out Of Here FAST! Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
